UC4--> Edit existing Contact with using their name
----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

mysql> update address_book set firstName='Madhu' where lastName='Naik';
Query OK, 1 row affected (0.02 sec)
Rows matched: 1  Changed: 1  Warnings: 0

